      "rationale": "The primary QoI is the normalized index of hemolysis derived from power-law integration of shear stress history along streamlines. This QoI is the standard metric for CFD-based hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance and directly supports the RH < 1 decision criterion. Gradation 2 achieved."
